It really is.

00:22:45.820 --> 00:22:48.700 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Not that the mainstream
medicine is bad by any means.

00:22:48.700 --> 00:22:49.760 align:middle line:84%
>>TODESCHI: No,
