He draws from it
in lots of ways.

00:22:51.134 --> 00:22:53.450 align:middle line:84%
But he draws from every
school of medicine.

00:22:53.450 --> 00:22:56.240 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: See, I've always
felt that, if you add holistic

00:22:56.240 --> 00:22:59.070 align:middle line:84%
with mainstream medicine,
