00:22:59.070 --> 00:22:59.870 align:middle line:90%
care of yourself.

00:22:59.870 --> 00:23:00.828 align:middle line:90%
>>TODESCHI: Absolutely.

00:23:00.828 --> 00:23:02.540 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: How old was
when he died, Kevin?

00:23:02.540 --> 00:23:03.640 align:middle line:90%
>>TODESCHI: He was 66.

00:23:03.640 --> 00:23:04.790 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Oh, that's young.

