>>TODESCHI: Yeah,
it's middle aged.

00:23:17.720 --> 00:23:19.070 align:middle line:90%
So he wore himself out.

00:23:19.070 --> 00:23:19.900 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: He did.

00:23:19.900 --> 00:23:20.750 align:middle line:84%
>>TODESCHI: And
when he passed away,

