And it wasn't really
until 1971 that they had

00:23:31.580 --> 00:23:34.010 align:middle line:90%
indexed all 14,000 readings.

00:23:34.010 --> 00:23:36.530 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Does anybody
else possess his ability

00:23:36.530 --> 00:23:37.580 align:middle line:90%
to do what he did?

