list of psychics

00:23:41.549 --> 00:23:43.340 align:middle line:84%
we work with that have
been on our programs

00:23:43.340 --> 00:23:45.320 align:middle line:90%
and are hopeful and positive.

00:23:45.320 --> 00:23:47.990 align:middle line:84%
And I've met many intuitives
who are extremely talented.

00:23:47.990 --> 00:23:50.240 align:middle line:84%
So yes, I think there are
people who help people.

00:23:50.240 --> 00:23:52.640 align:middle line:84%
I don't know of anybody who
does the range of topics

00:23:52.640 --> 00:23:53.610 align:middle line:90%
that he did, though.

00:23:53.610 --> 00:23:55.040 align:middle line:10%
>>NOORY: How many books
does he have out there--

00:23:55.040 --> 00:23:55.840 align:middle line:10%
Cayce?

00:23:55.840 --> 00:23:58.580 align:middle line:84%
>>TODESCHI: Cayce only
wrote one book on auras.

00:23:58.580 --> 00:24:01.910 align:middle line:84%
But there have been about 300
books written about Mr. Cayce.

00:24:01.910 --> 00:24:03.680 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Is this story true?

00:24:03.680 --> 00:24:06.710 align:middle line:84%
He was about to get
in an elevator, looked

00:24:06.710 --> 00:24:08.300 align:middle line:90%
at people in the elevator.

00:24:08.300 --> 00:24:09.800 align:middle line:90%
They had no aura.

00:24:09.800 --> 00:24:11.450 align:middle line:90%
He backed out.

00:24:11.450 --> 00:24:12.770 align:middle line:90%
He was scared.

00:24:12.770 --> 00:24:14.850 align:middle line:84%
The elevator crashed,
and they died.

00:24:14.850 --> 00:24:15.650 align:middle line:90%
Is that true?

00:24:15.650 --> 00:24:17.300 align:middle line:84%
>>TODESCHI: The story is
true, but it's not a story

00:24:17.300 --> 00:24:18.350 align:middle line:90%
that Edgar Cayce told.

00:24:18.350 --> 00:24:20.540 align:middle line:84%
It's a story another
psychic told Edgar Cayce.

00:24:20.540 --> 00:24:23.270 align:middle line:84%
And Edgar Cayce tells that
story in the book on auras--

00:24:23.270 --> 00:24:25.370 align:middle line:84%
about how the person
couldn't see any auras.

00:24:25.370 --> 00:24:27.910 align:middle line:84%
But it is a true story, but it
wasn't when Edgar Cayce said.

