and dream interpretation.

00:29:11.140 --> 00:29:14.320 align:middle line:84%
The dream state is one
of self-examination.

00:29:14.320 --> 00:29:17.500 align:middle line:10%
But it is also much
more, a storehouse

00:29:17.500 --> 00:29:23.090 align:middle line:10%
