Dreams can be a catalyst
for change in our lives.

00:29:37.980 --> 00:29:39.980 align:middle line:10%
They can also be
reaffirming that we

00:29:39.980 --> 00:29:41.600 align:middle line:10%
are headed in the
right direction--

00:29:41.600 --> 00:29:46.130 align:middle line:10%
that they can give us sort
of a spiritual upliftment

00:29:46.130 --> 00:29:49.820 align:middle line:10%
